                    <h1 class="SWWW_H1">Cookies and Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">Last updated: February 5, 2025</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">At Sustainable WWW, we care about your privacy and actively work to minimize data collection. This policy explains how we handle personal data and the use of cookies on our website sustainablewww.com.</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">2. Cookies</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">Our website does not use cookies for tracking, analytics, or personalization.</p>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">We use a static website hosted via an Express.js server. Additionally, we do not use sessions or other technologies that place cookies in your browser.</p>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">However, our website may be displayed through a cached version via Cloudflare, which may involve the use of technical cookies managed by Cloudflare to improve the website’s performance and security. These cookies are necessary for Cloudflare’s functionality and cannot be disabled.</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">3. Personal data</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">We do not collect personal data through the website, as we do not have contact forms or similar interactive features. If you wish to contact us, you must do so via your own email client or phone.</p>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">When you contact us via email or phone, we may store the following information:</p>
                    <ul class="SWWW_InfoList">
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Your name</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Your email address</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Your phone number</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Your company name (if applicable)</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Other information you choose to provide us</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">This information is used solely to respond to your inquiry and handle relevant matters. We store it only as long as necessary for the current case, after which it is deleted. This aligns with our environmental policy, as we avoid unnecessary data storage.</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">We do not share your information with third parties unless it is necessary to fulfill a legal obligation or an agreed-upon service.</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul class="SWWW_InfoList">
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Access the information we have about you.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Request correction or deletion of your information.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Object to the storage of your data.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">If you wish to exercise your rights, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:info@sustainablewww.org">info@sustainablewww.org</a>.</p>
                    <h2 class="SWWW_H2">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900">We may update this policy continuously to reflect changes in our practices or legislation. The latest version will always be available on our website.</p>
